#Purpose
The format of some of the predefined CDVI reports for site-wise swipe-in/swipe-out logs is ill suited for automated numerical calculation and analysis in Excel. This is an F# script that addresses that by parsing the CDVI CSV reports and reconstructs the data in a tabular format better suited to machine interpretation and pivot table use.
